模块 com.example.project3_studentroster
程序包 com.example.project3_studentroster

类 Roster

java.lang.Object
com.example.project3_studentroster.Roster
public class Roster extends Object
Manipulate the Student array that performs as a roster. Add, remove, and find students in the roster. Sort the roster by students' names or the last date they paid the fee Resize the array if more students are added.
作者:
Yuchen Wei, Denghao Sun

  • 方法详细资料

    • find

      private int find(Student student)
      The method to find if a student exists in the roster. Compare profiles of students to find.
      参数:
      student - to be found in the roster.
      返回:
      i, the index of the target student in the array, NOT_FOUND = -1 if a student is not in found the roster

    • grow

      private void grow()
      Expand the Student array by increasing the size by 4.

    • add

      public boolean add(Student student)
      Add a new student to the roster. Initialize the array if there is not a roster. Find if a student is already in the roster by using find() method, stop adding if one is. Expand the array if necessary by using grow() method.
      参数:
      student - to be added.
      返回:
      true if a student is successfully added, false if not.

    • remove

      public boolean remove(Student student)
      Remove a student from the roster if one exists in the roster.
      参数:
      student - is the target student to be removed.
      返回:
      true if a student is successfully removed, false if not.

    • getRoster

      public Student[] getRoster()
      Pass the private Student array, the roster out.
      返回:
      roster, the Student array.

    • getSize

      public int getSize()
      Pass the number of students in the roster out.
      返回:
      size, the length of the Student array.

    • compareName

      private int compareName(String student1, String student2)
      Helper method that determines the order of two names.
      参数:
      student1 - is the first student to be compared.
      student2 - is the second student to be compared.
      返回:
      1 if student1 is alphabetically ahead of student2, 0 if the two students have the same name, -1 if student2 is alphabetically ahead of student1,
